051458_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F051458_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b559f63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncooling落deepcool水冷<br />\n要超頻唔慳得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/051403_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F051403_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=33244005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nx79版，4ram slot, 2pciex16 slot<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/052839_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F052839_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c1735869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAdata ddr4 1600x4, 如果1600保證你打大部份game都唔會lag，2個dual channel就可以令你遊戲效能更上一層樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/051531_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F051531_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=47521a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nkingston ssd,<br />\n落夠兩隻120gb 行raid0<br />\n價錢更平，速度更快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/051634_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F051634_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=70cddf24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsegate 500hdd,<br />\n同上，落兩隻raid 0<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/051745_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F051745_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0e872b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重頭戲，兩張980ti sli<br />\n以確保4k gaming中高效都能達到流暢遊戲體驗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/051855_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F051855_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f4b8d423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n航嘉atx箱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/052056_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F052056_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3c85963c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火牛真係唔可以慳...所以忍痛上賊船 rm 850<br />\nrm850眾所周知係最穩定既model之一<br />\n加上850watt既out put,可以輕鬆推起粒3930k同兩張980ti之餘，仲可以再超頻<br />\n<br />\n加上靚火牛可以令你部機更穩定，壽命更長，所以寧願其他位將就少少都盡量用返隻靚d既牛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/052644_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F052644_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=dffb058a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個4k mon<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/054039_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F054039_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=688f743e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軟橋<br />\n<br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,盡左力，都係要爆左筆直，樓主都係將就下玩返1080p算啦"},{"pid":"a3233227af312abfe869598a2c16290dfa5470cb","tid":423740,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a72482ca18311724dcc463264335c5886cb1a7b","tid":423740,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"864f34da2cd460db87ee7ecad90e90acd083f334","tid":423740,"uid":51858,