穩定，壽命更長，所以寧願其他位將就少少都盡量用返隻靚d既牛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/052644_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F052644_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=dffb058a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個4k mon<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/054039_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F054039_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=688f743e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軟橋<br />\n<br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,盡左力，都係要爆左筆直，樓主都係將就下玩返1080p算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0f3dabb1aaae149924a1cf38732118033dd5d6","tid":423740,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1f25a5f52b2652928ed5320182eb81e191620b","tid":423740,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"i7 6950X +  ASUS GTX 1080Ti"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cbad0f122244078f193c3533047e8b6a8bf91f","tid":423740,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc97eae894ce0b3c6aaed42ab808334ae640e4f4","tid":423740,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"4k high <br />\n<br />\n大致上都係i7 8700k + 1080ti SLI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b778156fb409c2006e9102ebc096b8b4134ee52","tid":423740,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417ca44223f0bd44ba0cc0e8e89517